#META# contentSummary: An order sent from* al-Dīwān al-Ikhtiyārī *to the *muqaddams* and the people (*jamāʿat*) that appear in a certain list (tafṣīl), concerning the compensation for the sheep eaten by the villagers. The *dīwān* has sent Muʿtamid al-Dawla ʿAlī b. ʿAbd al-Rashīd to oversee the procedure.
